188
00:10:03,920 --> 00:10:04,480
Brother Lu.

189
00:10:04,730 --> 00:10:05,340
Seven days.

190
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:07,060
See you in seven days.

191
00:10:09,980 --> 00:10:10,900
Master.

192
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,610
