267
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:16,980
Okay.

268
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,320
Officer.

269
00:13:18,570 --> 00:13:19,050
Xue Huan.

270
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:19,930
